{"tid":148850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應對南亞人，新疆傳月薪五千包食宿招聘警員","createTime":"2017-03-08T23:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T16:31:01.000Z","uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"149b926f343685fdcd600659c48e3dd32181a077","tid":148850,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:13:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/354845-中國-重賞之下必有勇夫？新疆傳以5000元人民幣月薪招男警反恐維穩\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F354845-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%87%8D%E8%B3%9E%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%85%E6%9C%89%E5%8B%87%E5%A4%AB%EF%BC%9F%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%82%B3%E4%BB%A55000%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA%E6%8B%9B%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%A9&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b33ca5d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F354845-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%87%8D%E8%B3%9E%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%85%E6%9C%89%E5%8B%87%E5%A4%AB%EF%BC%9F%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%82%B3%E4%BB%A55000%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA%E6%8B%9B%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%A9&h=e2788154\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/354845-中國-重賞之下必有勇夫？新疆傳以5000元人民幣月薪招男警反恐維穩</a><br />\n<br />\n香港班猶太人覺得咁委屈，不如上去報效祖國啦"},{"pid":"455165ba4096f0f8cfac5f209d6d6c0ecab08760","tid":148850,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:29:31.000Z","msg":"可能要跟isis拼命，不了"},{"pid":"f825b39682041696772dde073e6c44360236e519","tid":148850,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:38:49.000Z","msg":"中國反恐重點地區新疆，近日傳出將以月薪5000元人民幣，招聘3000名男警參與反恐維穩工作，不但包食包住，更每月有額外500元人民幣的津貼。<br />\n相關的招聘廣告近日在網上廣傳，據悉，當局不限應徵者要高學歷，任何戶籍或民族亦可，而且退伍軍人優先。不過這份「筍工」潛在一定風險，因應聘者將被派往恐襲頻生的南疆喀什市駐守。<br />\n該招聘廣告顯示，新疆喀什市政府正招聘「便民警務站工作人員」，應聘者只要持大專及以上學歷便可申請，退伍軍人更放寬至高中學歷。招聘廣告顯示，將在全國招聘3000人，申請者的年齡需介乎18歲至35歲的男性，無違法犯罪記錄且身體健康。<br />\n至於待遇方面，應聘者可獲月薪5000元人民幣，另有500元人民幣的「維穩」津貼，並提供食宿，夫婦同赴喀什更可獲住房一套，如有需要政府甚至可為配偶安排工作職位；工作表現優異者更可按政策享受國家規定假期、報銷路費及調整工資。"},{"pid":"91612ee0b362458970e866b4b1a0db940d47b909","tid":148850,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:40:50.000Z","msg":"人命果然唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3781a9aed187afcd6bc11f1a979420afa9e958","tid":148850,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"我想問中東恐怖組織同南亞人有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418dce4c4072c9e6b6929994f8086c7efdc60bda","tid":148850,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問中東恐怖組織同南亞人有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無關係，應該係樓主玩針對"},{"pid":"3d1fa95b587d5cafba597d2d482e89d2eca348b1","tid":148850,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問中東恐怖組織同南亞人有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以連登仔既程度，兩樣咪差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93015882e7e98b7771a3da355d5a40ea8e6a191d","tid":148850,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問中東恐怖組織同南亞人有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im